Hazeel is a Zamorakian Mahjarrat, featured in the quest Hazeel Cult. Hazeel assisted Zamorak in his rebellion against Zaros. Towards the end of the Fourth Age, Hazeel dominated the region of Ardougne, until he was defeated by Saradominist peasants, led by the Carnillean family.

In the Hazeel Cult quest, the player has the option of reviving Hazeel, or preventing his return. If he is revived, Hazeel then heads to the north for the Mahjarrats' upcoming Ritual of Rejuvenation.

Hazeel emerges from his coffin.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Hazeel is an Arabic word meaning "emaciated".
